# Breadcrumb — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/breadcrumb.css`

## CSS Classes

- `.acko-breadcrumb` — nav wrapper, full width
- `.acko-breadcrumb-list` — flex row, items-center, flex-wrap, gap-1, no list style
- `.acko-breadcrumb-link` — body-sm font, `--color-breadcrumb-link`, hover underline, `transition: color 150ms`
- `.acko-breadcrumb-current` — label-lg weight, `--color-breadcrumb-current`, `aria-current="page"`
- `.acko-breadcrumb-separator-item` — flex, margin 0 space-1, `--color-breadcrumb-separator`
- `.acko-breadcrumb-ellipsis` — button, `padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-2)`, `border-radius: --radius-full`, hover `background: --color-surface-raised-hover`
- `.acko-breadcrumb-icon` — flex icon slot inside items

## Tokens Used

- `--color-breadcrumb-link`, `--color-breadcrumb-link-hover`, `--color-breadcrumb-current`
- `--color-breadcrumb-separator`, `--color-breadcrumb-text`
- `--color-surface-raised-hover` (ellipsis hover)
- `--font-body-sm-size`, `--font-label-lg-weight`
